{"comments":"BorderSide - single edge border configuration.\n\nA molecule combining border width, style, and color for one edge.\nThe fundamental unit of border composition.\n\n## Composition\n\n- BorderWidth: thickness in pixels (0.0 to finite)\n- BorderStyle: solid, dashed, dotted, etc.\n- Color: any color space (RGB used for interchange)\n\n## Usage\n\n```purescript\n-- Solid black border\ntopBorder = borderSide\n  { width: BorderWidth.thin\n  , style: Solid\n  , color: rgb 0 0 0\n  }\n\n-- Dashed accent border\naccentBorder = borderSideDashed (borderWidth 2.0) accentColor\n```\n\n## Dependencies\n\n- Hydrogen.Schema.Surface.BorderWidth\n- Hydrogen.Schema.Color.RGB\n","declarations":[{"children":[{"comments":null,"info":{"arguments":[],"declType":"dataConstructor"},"sourceSpan":{"end":[87,9],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Surface/BorderSide.purs","start":[87,3]},"title":"None"},{"comments":null,"info":{"arguments":[],"declType":"dataConstructor"},"sourceSpan":{"end":[88,11],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Surface/BorderSide.purs","start":[88,3]},"title":"Hidden"},{"comments":null,"info":{"arguments":[],"declType":"dataConstructor"},"sourceSpan":{"end":[89,10],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Surface/BorderSide.purs","start":[89,3]},"title":"Solid"},{"comments":null,"info":{"arguments":[],"declType":"dataConstructor"},"sourceSpan":{"end":[90,11],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Surface/BorderSide.purs","start":[90,3]},"title":"Dashed"},{"comments":null,"info":{"arguments":[],"declType":"dataConstructor"},"sourceSpan":{"end":[91,11],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Surface/BorderSide.purs","start":[91,3]},"title":"Dotted"},{"comments":null,"info":{"arguments":[],"declType":"dataConstructor"},"sourceSpan":{"end":[92,11],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Surface/BorderSide.purs","start":[92,3]},"title":"Double"},{"comments":null,"info":{"arguments":[],"declType":"dataConstructor"},"sourceSpan":{"end":[93,1